# Styling Conventions

- Tailwind CSS v4 with custom CSS variables in [globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)
- Use `bg-accent` instead of `bg-[var(--accent)]` for CSS variables
- Glass effects: `.glass-transparent` and `.glass-solid` classes available
- Button variants: `.btn`, `.btn-primary`, `.btn-ghost`
- Motion animations via `motion/react` library